Name: Invoice
Description: An agent that processes invoices and manages billing tasks. This can talk to multiple systems and get the relevant responses for you.

Capabilities.Name: ProcessInvoice
Capabilities.Description: Processes an invoice and returns the status.

Capabilities.Name: Billing management
Capabilities.Description: Retrieves the current billing status for a customer.

Capabilities.Name: Payment tracking
Capabilities.Description: Tracks payment status and updates the invoice accordingly.

Name: CustomerSupport
Description: An agent that handles customer support queries and issues.

Capabilities.Name: HandleQuery
Capabilities.Description: Handles customer queries and provides relevant information.

Capabilities.Name: ResolveIssue
Capabilities.Description: Resolves customer issues and updates the ticket status.
